item.title: Hello i asking how ti change my spell!
item.dc:creator: @x_sam_x1 x sam x
item.description:
@x_sam_x1 wrote:

Dastan is right but ill explain it better,
if you want to change the name of the teleport it is in text handler (you can just search the name of the teleport you want to change)
If you want to change the coordinates of where the teleport takes you to you go into clickingmost.java or clicking.java, and search case 4146 (that is where the teleports start, or you can search the coordinates where it takes you to.) Then you change the coordinates to where you want the teleport to take you.
hope i helped
